  - guid: 9e6f961a-2cbe-4cf2-b216-301a6bf3be0c
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Hah. You might have won this battle.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: But I gotcha.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: We did get some money out of you here. As the gamblers
        say, the bank always wins!
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: I will admit, you are indeed strong. Not many have
        beat me in battle, even with help.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: That won't change anything though. We'll have a little
        server maintenance and I'll be back.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: It's too bad I don't see you being a high performer
        when it comes to making cash. You will agree with me on that.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Which means we'll have to bench you. Hopefully the
        next update will bring a more profitable girl.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: And one more thing, Asuka.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You really came all this way just for not sticking
        to your ideals when it matters most?
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 280, y: 200}
